		<p class="mb_50 fs_18 te-bn-text"><p class="mb_30 fs_22 fw_medium c_light">ALIMatar Construction Ltd, a merger of Head Office &amp; General Construction and General Contractors, has excelled in residential contracting in Cyprus's Paphos area for 11 years. In response to local business growth and a desire for higher profitability, the company is shifting its focus from residential to commercial clients. Their strategic plan outlines the steps to succeed in this competitive market, backed by a dedicated 24/7 team. Their services include general construction, building projects, remodeling, permitting, site preparations, carpentry, cement foundations, painting, plumbing, utilities installation, swimming pool construction, and insulation. Additionally, ALIMatar Construction is open to subcontracting opportunities, offering its expertise to other businesses.</p>            </div>   
    
